legs.start_address: Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes, 2, 08010 Barcelona, Spain

steps.html_instructions:
Head northeast on Gran Via de les Corts Catalanes/Plaça de Tetuan toward Passeig de Sant Joan
Continue to follow Plaça de Tetuan
At Plaça de Francesc Macià, take the 3rd exit and stay on Avinguda Diagonal
Keep left to continue on B-23, follow signs for E-90/Lleida/Zaragoza/Tarragona

Keep left to stay on B-23
Toll road

Keep left to stay on AP-7
Toll road

Take the E-90/AP-2 exit toward Lleida/Zaragoza
Toll road
Take the E-90/A-2 exit toward La Almunia de Doña Godina/Madrid

Merge onto Calle de O'Donnell/M-23
Continue to follow Calle de O'Donnell
Continue straight to stay on Calle de O'Donnell
Calle de Alcalá turns slightly right and becomes Plaza de la Independencia
Slight right to stay on Calle de Alcalá

Slight right onto Calle Gran Vía
Destination will be on the right
